---
// Debug page to verify Clerk configuration
const pubKey = import.meta.env.PUBLIC_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY;
const secretKey = import.meta.env.CLERK_SECRET_KEY;
---

<html>
<head>
    <title>Clerk Configuration Debug</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Clerk Configuration Debug</h1>
    
    <div style="background: #f0f0f0; padding: 1rem; margin: 1rem 0; border-radius: 4px;">
        <h2>Environment Variables</h2>
        <p><strong>Publishable Key:</strong></p>
        <code style="background: white; padding: 0.5rem; display: block; margin: 0.5rem 0;">
            {pubKey || 'NOT SET'}
        </code>
        
        <p><strong>Secret Key (first 20 chars):</strong></p>
        <code style="background: white; padding: 0.5rem; display: block; margin: 0.5rem 0;">
            {secretKey ? secretKey.substring(0, 20) + '...' : 'NOT SET'}
        </code>
    </div>
    
    <div style="background: #e6f3ff; padding: 1rem; margin: 1rem 0; border-radius: 4px;">
        <h2>How to Verify Correct Clerk App</h2>
        <ol>
            <li><strong>Copy your publishable key above</strong></li>
            <li><strong>Go to <a href="https://dashboard.clerk.com" target="_blank">Clerk Dashboard</a></strong></li>
            <li><strong>Check each application's API Keys</strong></li>
            <li><strong>Find the app with the matching publishable key</strong></li>
            <li><strong>That's where your users are being created!</strong></li>
        </ol>
    </div>
    
    <div style="background: #fff3cd; padding: 1rem; margin: 1rem 0; border-radius: 4px;">
        <h2>Expected Key Format</h2>
        <p>Your publishable key should:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Start with <code>pk_test_</code> (for test environment)</li>
            <li>Or <code>pk_live_</code> (for production)</li>
            <li>Match exactly with your intended Clerk application</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    
    <div style="background: #d4edda; padding: 1rem; margin: 1rem 0; border-radius: 4px;">
        <h2>Quick Test</h2>
        <p>If users are signing up successfully but not appearing in your dashboard:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>‚úÖ Clerk integration is working</li>
            <li>‚ùå You're looking at the wrong Clerk application</li>
            <li>üîç Use the publishable key above to find the correct app</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    
    <p><a href="/">Back to Home</a> | <a href="/sign-up">Test Sign Up</a></p>
</body>
</html>